Raising tiny humans without losing my mind 📚✨ These gems are basically my survival manuals: The Whole-Brain Child, How to Talk So Kids Will Listen, and The Conscious Parent.
a few other great parenting reads are-
📔How to Talk so Little Kids will Listen- because before getting them to talk, we need to get them to listen 😅
📕Boy Mum- An insightful book on parenting boys and ways we can meet their emotional needs
📗The Gardener and the Carpenter- a thought-provoking book about letting go of perfectionism and trusting the process of growth.
